pr_title: Adding support to PAPPL for converting non-eSCL scanners to eSCL Servers
pr_body: @tillkamppeter @michaelrsweet  This is an update on the documentation aspect of scanning in PAPPL. The document generation was done using code-doc. Also additional changes have been made in pappl-body.md to update the scanning implementation. With this now we have a clear insight on the issue #130 and the changes that are to be implemented.
